metadata.name: Blobs Duchy #1
metadata.description: BLOBS DUCHY is a collection of 15,555 randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum Blockchain. BLOBS NFT is a gateway for DUCHY (Dukes World/ Dukes Territory/Community Membership), which grants access to several kinds of Passive Incomes, NFT Staking, Buybacks, Duchy roles and Special benefits like Royalty fee sharing upto 60%, Profit sharing upto 30% gift vouchers, giveaways from competitions, free project promotion and project collaboration for holders. Future details are updated in the official website & discord community through the Roadmap. Visit www.duchycreations.com for more details.
